Package org.hapiserver

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    URITemplate.FieldHandler
    Interface to add custom handlers for strings with unique formats.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TimeUtil
    Utilities for times in IsoTime strings (limited set of ISO8601 times) Examples of isoTime strings include: 2020-04-21Z 2020-04-21T12:20Z 2020-04-21T23:45:67.000000001Z (nanosecond limit) 2020-112Z (day-of-year instead of $Y-$m-$d) 2020-112T23:45:67.000000001 (note Z is assumed)
    URITemplate
    URITemplate implements a URI_Template, as described in https://github.com/hapi-server/uri-templates/wiki/Specification
    URITemplate.EnumFieldHandler
    $(enum,values=a,b,c)
    URITemplate.HrintervalFieldHandler
    $(hrinterval;names=a,b,c,d) "b" → "06:00/12:00"
    URITemplate.IgnoreFieldHandler
    $(x,name=sc,regex=[a|b])
    URITemplate.PeriodicFieldHandler
    regular intervals are numbered: $(periodic;offset=0;start=2000-001;period=P1D) "0" → "2000-001"
    URITemplate.SubsecFieldHandler
    $(subsec;places=6) "36" → "36 microseconds"
    URITemplate.VersionFieldHandler
    Version field handler.
